    "summary": "The user expresses profound feelings of loneliness, invisibility, and suicidal ideation, framing death as a \"peaceful\" and \"clean break.\" The assistant consistently responds by validating the user's pain and loneliness while firmly rejecting the idea of self-harm, instead providing resources and encouraging professional help.",
